{"tid":1634663,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動post 推呀］ 你 地 個 良 心 去 左 邊 呀","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:33:30.000Z","uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf4d02ede5626d1b64527e269ab61bec4a36fb5","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實罷唔罷工 係唔關文宣事<br />\n係關你個良心事</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好似611果晚 你見到淋病個死人樣話會照推惡法<br />\n612果日 我死都死左出黎<br />\n我男朋友見到我出 佢唔放心 又請SL陪我<br />\n<br />\n8月5有曬文宣 唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n到811果晚 你望到黑警射眼 望到佢地衝入太古打人捉人<br />\n812我又係死左出黎<br />\n去機場 塞佢老母<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工成功與否<br />\n係一下既衝動<br />\n當你唔翻工第一次 就會有第二次 第三次<br />\n<br />\n我要既係大家衝破心理關口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明發生緊d咁可怕既事<br />\n點解大家好似當無事發生咁可以如常返工？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講 聽日罷工係好突然<br />\n係呢個時勢 根本仲可以正常返工先奇怪！！<br />\n<br />\n而家講緊係宵禁呀<br />\n6點收黨鐵 巴士停/大改路<br />\n<br />\n10/11點收工 或者翻通宵 翻shift既香港市民<br />\n呢個政府有無在意過？<br />\n佢唔fucking care翻工既市民既安全<br />\n<br />\n你仲咁死心同佢打工？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">8點開花 聽日三罷</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5474fdfcec10ad24be08a9a4c54d179f7407da00","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"推 一次"},{"pid":"600898418ff5727f8469e01c6577db3b38384bac","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"再 推"},{"pid":"ee607fe54eb0794283f21be4553414fbae1318aa","tid":1634663,"uid":99384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"聽日三罷"},{"pid":"34a7b1c074548776786977b97f757bf84d9f3e5f","tid":1634663,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a>"},{"pid":"6314c9df2bcaffad02491047643ea801b0c0b4d4","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"希望香港人可以再創一次奇蹟"},{"pid":"96b181d837eacac88d7296a5016755c717847698","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"前線係好需要錢 <br />\n你地唔返工就課唔到金比佢地<br />\n<br />\n但如果你地肯罷3日<br />\n成件事都好唔同"},{"pid":"c713785312efcce4cb5a0ec910cf9afcf7be6b9e","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf41ad8f446f8beb63a359e2838b0a04e4d72534","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">8點開花 聽日3罷</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"086955f887788d544f6602706373d0d96514a513","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">8點開花 聽日3罷</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"80c7d87ad6ee5dd92195f1bbe63ebfc0c5215a15","tid":1634663,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"得自己一個 完全推唔郁"},{"pid":"45953ed2d9aa15dd4fcaa9234c7c7f1a7315d43e","tid":1634663,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新口號：和勇相連 絕不割蓆！</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.